{"article_id":"N55n5UVeAZHWSSva","edus":[{"id":0,"text":"Supreme Court Justice Ruth Bader Ginsburg faced a growing and bipartisan backlash Wednesday","depth":4},{"id":1,"text":"-- including a call from Donald Trump","depth":5},{"id":2,"text":"to resign --","depth":5},{"id":3,"text":"as she doubled down on her criticism of the presumptive GOP nominee ,","depth":4},{"id":4,"text":"calling him a \" faker \"","depth":5},{"id":5,"text":"who is unqualified to be president .","depth":5},{"id":6,"text":"Even political figures and newspaper editorial writers","depth":4},{"id":7,"text":"who might agree with the comments","depth":4},{"id":8,"text":"swiftly said","depth":4},{"id":9,"text":"they were out of line for a high court justice .","depth":4},{"id":10,"text":"The liberal icon justice had kicked off the storm with comments to The New York Times","depth":6},{"id":11,"text":"published Saturday .","depth":6},{"id":12,"text":"\" I can ' t imagine what this place would be -","depth":9},{"id":13,"text":"I can ' t imagine what the country would be --","depth":9},{"id":14,"text":"with Donald Trump as our president .","depth":8},{"id":15,"text":"For the country , it could be four years .","depth":8},{"id":16,"text":"For the court , it could be --","depth":9},{"id":17,"text":"I don ' t even want to contemplate that , \"","depth":9},{"id":18,"text":"she said .","depth":6},{"id":19,"text":"She doubled down late Monday ,","depth":6},{"id":20,"text":"telling CNN :","depth":7},{"id":21,"text":"\" He is a faker . ''","depth":7},{"id":22,"text":"`` He has no consistency about him .","depth":8},{"id":23,"text":"He says whatever comes into his head at the moment .","depth":8},{"id":24,"text":"He really has an ego . ...","depth":7},{"id":25,"text":"How has he gotten away with not turning over his tax returns ?","depth":8},{"id":26,"text":"The press seems to be very gentle with him on that , ''","depth":8},{"id":27,"text":"she said .","depth":7},{"id":28,"text":"Trump swiftly responded Tuesday ,","depth":5},{"id":29,"text":"telling the Times","depth":6},{"id":30,"text":"it was \" highly inappropriate that a United States Supreme Court judge gets involved in a political campaign . \"","depth":6},{"id":31,"text":"\" I think","depth":7},{"id":32,"text":"it ' s a disgrace to the court","depth":7},{"id":33,"text":"and I think","depth":7},{"id":34,"text":"she should apologize to the court .","depth":7},{"id":35,"text":"I couldn ' t believe it","depth":7},{"id":36,"text":"when I saw it , \"","depth":7},{"id":37,"text":"the presumptive Republican nominee said .","depth":6},{"id":38,"text":"Trump ' s criticisms were echoed by Republican congressional leaders .","depth":5},{"id":39,"text":"Senate Majority Leader Mitch McConnell said Tuesday","depth":7},{"id":40,"text":"Ginsburg ' s comments were `` totally inappropriate . \"","depth":7},{"id":41,"text":"`` It raises a level of skepticism","depth":8},{"id":42,"text":"that the American people have from time to time about just how objective the Supreme Court is ,","depth":9},{"id":43,"text":"whether they 're over there","depth":10},{"id":44,"text":"to call the balls and strikes ,","depth":11},{"id":45,"text":"or weigh in on one side or another , ''","depth":11},{"id":46,"text":"he said .","depth":7},{"id":47,"text":"House Speaker Paul Ryan used similar language at a CNN event Tuesday .","depth":6},{"id":48,"text":"`` For someone on the Supreme Court","depth":9},{"id":49,"text":"who is going to be calling balls and strikes in the future","depth":10},{"id":50,"text":"based upon whatever the next president and Congress does ,","depth":10},{"id":51,"text":"that strikes me as inherently biased and out of the realm , ''","depth":8},{"id":52,"text":"Ryan said .","depth":7},{"id":53,"text":"\" We all know","depth":9},{"id":54,"text":"that the justices on the Supreme Court have political views .","depth":9},{"id":55,"text":"I ' m not sure","depth":9},{"id":56,"text":"we ' re well served","depth":10},{"id":57,"text":"by them airing them out in the open , \"","depth":10},{"id":58,"text":"Sen. Chris Murphy , D-Conn. , told Politico .","depth":7},{"id":59,"text":"\" She may have got out over her skis a little bit and more forthright and political","depth":9},{"id":60,"text":"than she should have been .","depth":9},{"id":61,"text":"It ' s very unusual , \"","depth":8},{"id":62,"text":"Senate Minority Whip Dick Durbin , D-Ill. , told the outlet .","depth":7},{"id":63,"text":"Mainstream media outlets also joined in the chorus of criticism .","depth":5},{"id":64,"text":"\" However valid her comments may have been , though ,","depth":9},{"id":65,"text":"and however","depth":10},{"id":66,"text":"in keeping with her known political bent ,","depth":11},{"id":67,"text":"they were still much , much better left unsaid by a member of the Supreme Court , \"","depth":11},{"id":68,"text":"The Washington Post ' s editorial board said Tuesday .","depth":8},{"id":69,"text":"\" Politicization , real or perceived , undermines public faith in the impartiality of the courts . \"","depth":8},{"id":70,"text":"The board noted","depth":9},{"id":71,"text":"the Code of Conduct for U.S. judges says","depth":10},{"id":72,"text":"that a \" judge should not . . . publicly endorse or oppose a candidate for public office . \"","depth":10},{"id":73,"text":"The New York Times also chimed in :","depth":7},{"id":74,"text":"\" Washington is more than partisan enough","depth":8},{"id":75,"text":"without the spectacle","depth":9},{"id":76,"text":"of a Supreme Court justice","depth":10},{"id":77,"text":"flinging herself into the mosh pit . ''","depth":10},{"id":78,"text":"Wednesday morning brought some relief for the under-fire justice ,","depth":6},{"id":79,"text":"with Vermont Sen. Bernie Sanders giving qualified support for her comments .","depth":6},{"id":80,"text":"While the Democratic presidential candidate declined to comment on whether her comments were appropriate ,","depth":6},{"id":81,"text":"he said on ABC","depth":8},{"id":82,"text":"he agrees","depth":9},{"id":83,"text":"Trump is a `` total opportunist ''","depth":9},{"id":84,"text":"and said","depth":8},{"id":85,"text":"`` the record is quite clear","depth":9},{"id":86,"text":"that he lies just a whole lot of the time . ''","depth":9}],"relations":[{"parent":173,"left":96,"right":172,"relation":"elaboration","nuclearity":"NS"},{"parent":96,"left":92,"right":95,"relation":"elaboration","nuclearity":"NS"},{"parent":92,"left":89,"right":91,"relation":"context","nuclearity":"NS"},{"parent":89,"left":0,"right":88,"relation":"elaboration","nuclearity":"NS"},{"parent":88,"left":1,"right":2,"relation":"purpose","nuclearity":"NS"},{"parent":91,"left":3,"right":90,"relation":"elaboration","nuclearity":"NS"},{"parent":90,"left":4,"right":5,"relation":"elaboration","nuclearity":"NS"},{"parent":95,"left":93,"right":94,"relation":"same-unit","nuclearity":"NN"},{"parent":93,"left":6,"right":7,"relation":"elaboration","nuclearity":"NS"},{"parent":94,"left":8,"right":9,"relation":"attribution","nuclearity":"SN"},{"parent":172,"left":123,"right":171,"relation":"joint","nuclearity":"NN"},{"parent":123,"left":113,"right":122,"relation":"joint","nuclearity":"NN"},{"parent":113,"left":104,"right":112,"relation":"joint","nuclearity":"NN"},{"parent":104,"left":97,"right":103,"relation":"organization","nuclearity":"SN"},{"parent":97,"left":10,"right":11,"relation":"elaboration","nuclearity":"NS"},{"parent":103,"left":102,"right":18,"relation":"attribution","nuclearity":"NS"},{"parent":102,"left":99,"right":101,"relation":"elaboration","nuclearity":"NS"},{"parent":99,"left":98,"right":14,"relation":"same-unit","nuclearity":"NN"},{"parent":98,"left":12,"right":13,"relation":"restatement","nuclearity":"NN"},{"parent":101,"left":15,"right":100,"relation":"joint","nuclearity":"NN"},{"parent":100,"left":16,"right":17,"relation":"organization","nuclearity":"SN"},{"parent":112,"left":106,"right":111,"relation":"elaboration","nuclearity":"NS"},{"parent":106,"l